metadata.name: Mysterious connection 1.0
metadata.description:
Mysterious connection was created by Marta Khmilyar (Smbwhodraws)

The goal of this collection is to show the connection between human and their totem animal inside. It's a little bit about the mystery and magic inside everybody!

Colors play here an essential part in both atmosphere and emotional portrait.

This project includes six works of art!

4500x4500
